<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:12:21 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>未连接的点</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3a8632bede2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;点。未连接。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Closeup of a laptop keyboard. A red dot in between." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a3a8632bede2.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:12:21 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>暑期游泳计划</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3a7421f1e61</link><description>&lt;p&gt;站在社区泳池浅水区边缘，旁边立着一块"禁止跳水"的标牌。我们入会已有一阵子，但游泳的次数并没有我想要的那么多。今年夏天，我想把每周去游泳变成我的日常习惯。这不仅是很好的锻炼，也是多出门走走的好借口。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='Bare feet standing near a pool edge with a clear "No Diving" sign in bold black letters. The blue water contrasts with the concrete surface.' height="2910" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3a7421f1e61.jpg" width="3886"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 11:55:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3a4e345a7ef</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这是以俄亥俄州萨菲尔德为基地的Wingfoot One（N1A），靠近固特异公司位于阿克伦的总部。

如果你读到这里心想，*那不是软式飞艇，而是半刚性飞艇*，你说得没错。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A Goodyear blimp floats in a bright blue sky with white clouds, photographed from below with tree branches visible in the foreground." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/6a3a4e345a7ef.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 09:13:28 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>雨前的鹭鸟</title><link>https://some.pics/6a39f9261dbad</link><description>&lt;p&gt;雨前的苍鹭。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Heron, before the rain hit. " height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pedalgr/6a39f9261dbad.jpg" width="2268"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pedalgr.some.pics"&gt;@pedalgr&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 03:10:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>钢琴手</title><link>https://some.pics/6a39bdcbb9496</link><description>&lt;p&gt;钢琴手&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Piano hands" height="3888" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a39bdcbb9496.jpg" width="5184"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 22:57:22 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>